pages.text: $(#e2a3ff)$(l:https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/texture-packs/nautilus3d)Nautilus3D$()$(br2)From their project page, “Combining the classic look of Minecraft with simple, yet detailed 3D models, Nautilus 3D gives everyones favourite sandbox game a more defined and intricate look.” 3D may sound like too much, it adds just enough detail to everything to preserve the vanilla look and feel.
